Facebook, hi, until a few days ago i had several "extra" feeds of my own where i hade collected different dependending on subject. one was literature where i had several publishing houses, magazines of literature etc. now i cannot find my feeds. what have you done with them?
I've tried to contact you on messenger, but so far no answer. 
I really would like to have them back as i very much enjoy reading them. 
Now, where can I find them again?
Yours, 
Johan
